---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BackButton from "../components/BackButton.astro";

const meta = [
  { label: "Year", value: "2022" },
  { label: "Client", value: "The Sofa & Chair Company" },
  { label: "Role", value: "Lead Product Designer" },
  { label: "Timeline", value: "12 months" },
];

const stats = [
  { value: "700+", label: "Artboards" },
  { value: "7", label: "Viewports" },
  { value: "12mo", label: "End-to-end build" },
  { value: "1", label: "Sole designer" },
];
---

<Layout title="Larkbury — Sammy Norris">

  <!-- Back nav -->
  <nav class="case-nav">
    <BackButton />
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="hero">
    <span class="hero__eyebrow b3" data-reveal>Case study — 04</span>

    <h1 class="hero__title" data-reveal style="--delay: 0.06s">
      Larkbury
    </h1>

    <p class="hero__lede" data-reveal style="--delay: 0.14s">
      A luxury brand built from scratch.
    </p>

    <dl class="hero__meta" data-reveal style="--delay: 0.22s">
      {meta.map((item) => (
        <div class="hero__meta-row">
          <dt class="b4">{item.label}</dt>
          <dd class="b3">{item.value}</dd>
        </div>
      ))}
    </dl>

    <p class="hero__desc b1" data-reveal style="--delay: 0.3s">
      A high-end luxury home and interiors brand built from scratch — brand
      identity and ecommerce site designed solo across 700+ artboards and
      seven viewports.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Figure 01 — hero shot -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-1-m.jpg" />
      <img src="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-1.jpg" alt="Larkbury London brand hero" loading="eager" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter I — Challenge -->
  <section class="chapter" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num">I.</span>
      <span class="chapter__label b2">The challenge</span>
    </header>

    <blockquote class="chapter__quote">
      Larkbury London didn't exist before this project. The brief was to
      create it — from the ground up — and to do it in a way that could hold
      its own in the high-end interiors market.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="chapter__body">
      <p class="b1">
        Working as the sole designer over twelve months, the scope covered
        everything from foundational brand decisions through to a fully
        responsive ecommerce site built on a custom platform. Seven viewports
        meant designing for every context a customer might encounter the
        brand — ensuring the luxury positioning translated consistently
        whether someone was browsing on a large desktop display or a phone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 02 -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-2-m.jpg" />
      <img src="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-2.jpg" alt="Larkbury brand and identity work" loading="lazy" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter II — Process -->
  <section class="chapter" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num">II.</span>
      <span class="chapter__label b2">The process</span>
    </header>

    <h2 class="chapter__h2">
      Seven hundred artboards, <em>one designer.</em>
    </h2>

    <div class="chapter__body">
      <p class="b1">
        The scale of the project was significant. Over 700 artboards
        documented the full design system and ecommerce experience, covering
        the breadth of templates, states, and interactions needed to hand
        off a production-ready build. Designing at that level of fidelity
        solo required a structured approach — building out components and
        patterns early that could scale across the full site without
        becoming inconsistent.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 03 -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-3-m.jpg" />
      <img src="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-3.jpg" alt="Larkbury ecommerce screens" loading="lazy" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter III — Outcome -->
  <section class="chapter chapter--outcome" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num">III.</span>
      <span class="chapter__label b2">The outcome</span>
    </header>

    <h2 class="chapter__h2">
      Restraint <em>doing the heavy lifting.</em>
    </h2>

    <div class="stats">
      {stats.map((s) => (
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__value">{s.value}</span>
          <span class="stat__label b3">{s.label}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="chapter__body chapter__body--double">
      <p class="b1">
        The design needed to feel restrained and considered rather than
        feature-heavy, with typography, whitespace, and imagery doing the
        heavy lifting. Informal testing throughout helped sense-check
        decisions — particularly around the purchase journey, where friction
        at any point risks undermining the premium experience the brand was
        built on.
      </p>
      <p class="b1">
        Larkbury London has since launched, and the finished product reflects
        the ambition of the original brief — a brand and digital presence
        that feels genuinely considered from the first touchpoint to the
        last.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 04 -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-4-m.jpg" />
      <img src="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-4.jpg" alt="Larkbury responsive site" loading="lazy" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Figure 05 -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-5-m.jpg" />
      <img src="/images/projects/larkbury/image-larkbury-5.jpg" alt="Larkbury detail work" loading="lazy" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <section class="closing" data-reveal>
    <p class="closing__signoff">
      <em>Designed at The Sofa &amp; Chair Company</em>, 2022.
    </p>
    <a href="/#work" class="closing__cta" aria-label="Return to all work">
      <span class="closing__cta-icon">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M5 12l7 7M5 12l7-7" />
        </svg>
      </span>
      <span class="closing__cta-label">Return to all work</span>
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="case-footer">
    <span class="b4">&copy; 2026 Sammy Norris</span>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("revealed");
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: "0px 0px -40px 0px" }
  );
  document.querySelectorAll("[data-reveal]").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>

<style>
  /* ===================== Back nav ===================== */
  .case-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 24px;
    left: 24px;
    z-index: 100;
  }

  /* ===================== Hero ===================== */
  .hero {
    padding: 160px 10vw 128px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero__eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .hero__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .hero__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 48px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .hero__meta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin: 0 0 64px;
    padding: 32px 10vw;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
  }

  .hero__meta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .hero__meta-row dt {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero__meta-row dd {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero__desc {
    max-width: calc(56ch + 160px);
  }

  /* ===================== Figures ===================== */
  .figure {
    margin: 0 0 96px;
    padding: 0 10vw;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .figure > picture {
    display: block;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 8px;
  }

  .figure + .figure {
    margin-top: -64px;
  }

  .figure picture > img,
  .figure > img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 18px;
  }

  /* ===================== Chapters ===================== */
  .chapter {
    margin: 0 0 96px;
    padding: 0 10vw;
  }

  .chapter__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
  }

  .chapter__num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .chapter__label {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .chapter__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0 0 64px;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    max-width: 80%;
  }

  .chapter__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .chapter__h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .chapter__body {
    max-width: calc(56ch + 160px);
  }

  .chapter__body--double {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  /* ===================== Stats ===================== */
  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 0 0 96px;
    padding: 48px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .stat__value {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .stat__label {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.55;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ===================== Closing ===================== */
  .closing {
    margin: 0 0 96px;
    padding: 96px 10vw 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 12%, transparent);
  }

  .closing__signoff {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .closing__signoff em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .closing__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 4px 16px 4px 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
    border-radius: 99px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .closing__cta:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .closing__cta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-b3);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .closing__cta-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background-color: var(--color-card-image-bg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===================== Footer ===================== */
  .case-footer {
    padding: 64px 10vw;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ===================== Scroll reveal ===================== */
  [data-reveal] {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition:
      opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) var(--delay, 0s),
      transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) var(--delay, 0s);
  }

  [data-reveal].revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ===================== Mobile ===================== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .b1 { font-size: var(--text-b2); }

    .case-nav {
      top: 20px;
      left: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 96px 20px 80px;
    }

    .hero__eyebrow {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero__title {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 11vw, 3.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero__lede {
      font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 4.5vw, 1.375rem);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .hero__meta {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px 16px;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero__desc {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .figure {
      padding: 0 16px;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .figure + .figure {
      margin-top: -44px;
    }

    .chapter {
      padding: 0 20px;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .chapter__head {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .chapter__num {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .chapter__quote {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 5.5vw, 1.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .chapter__h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.625rem, 7vw, 2rem);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .chapter__body--double {
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px 16px;
      padding: 32px 0;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .stat {
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .stat__value {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 9vw, 2.5rem);
    }

    .closing {
      padding: 64px 20px 0;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .case-footer {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
